The article consists of a collection of statements and endorsements from various individuals supporting Gina Haspel, President Trump's nominee for the Director of the Central Intelligence Agency (CIA). The statements come from politicians, former CIA directors, intelligence professionals, national security officials, commentators, and thinkers. They highlight Haspel's qualifications, experience, leadership skills, and dedication to the national security of the United States. Many emphasize her expertise in intelligence, her integrity, and her commitment to the mission of the CIA. The statements aim to provide a positive view of Haspel and support her nomination for the position.